### 5. Scheduler (`kernel/src/proc/sched.rs`)

**`rts_set` signature (lines 180-188):**
```rust
pub unsafe fn rts_set(p: &mut Proc, flag: u32) {
    let was_runnable = p.rts_flags.load(Ordering::Relaxed) == 0;
    p.rts_flags.fetch_or(flag, Ordering::Relaxed);
    let nr = p.nr;
    if was_runnable {
        unsafe { dequeue(nr) }
    }
}
```
Sets bits in `p.rts_flags`; if proc was runnable (all-clear), dequeues it from the run queue.

**`rts_unset` signature (lines 200-208):**
```rust
pub unsafe fn rts_unset(p: &mut Proc, flag: u32) {
    let prev = p.rts_flags.fetch_and(!flag, Ordering::Relaxed);
    let nr = p.nr;
    let now_runnable = (prev & !flag) == 0;
    if now_runnable && prev != 0 {
        unsafe { enqueue(nr) }
    }
}
```
Clears bits in `p.rts_flags`; if proc transitions from blocked to runnable (all bits cleared), enqueues it.

